{"id":2560,"date":"2022-05-05T15:09:27","date_gmt":"2022-05-05T08:09:27","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2560"},"modified":"2023-09-18T15:10:15","modified_gmt":"2023-09-18T08:10:15","slug":"thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-dai-hoc-chinh-quy-nganh-ngon-ngu-anh-nam-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/thong-bao-tuyen-sinh-dai-hoc-chinh-quy-nganh-ngon-ngu-anh-nam-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"TH\u00d4NG B\u00c1O TUY\u1ec2N SINH \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC CH\u00cdNH QUY NG\u00c0NH NG\u00d4N NG\u1eee ANH N\u0102M 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"single-latest-text\">\n<div class=\"single-item-comment-view d-none\"><strong style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">1. \u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><br \/>\n<i class=\"zmdi zmdi-calendar-check\"><\/i><\/div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Th\u00ed sinh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2.1<em>.X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n<\/em><\/strong> <strong><em>theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp THPT<\/em><\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: white;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111i\u1ec3m trung b\u00ecnh 3 m\u00f4n x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a 03 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 (2 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 l\u1edbp 11v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 1 l\u1edbp 12) <strong>ho\u1eb7c<\/strong> n\u0103m l\u1edbp 12 + \u0111i\u1ec3m \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3) \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1eeb 15<strong>\u00a0\u0111i\u1ec3m<\/strong> tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>T\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n:<br \/>\nD<\/strong><\/em><strong><em>01<\/em><\/strong><strong><em>: <\/em><\/strong><em>To\u00e1n,<\/em><em>V\u0103n,Ti\u1ebfng Anh, <strong>D07:<\/strong> To\u00e1n, H\u00f3a, Ti\u1ebfng Anh,<\/em><br \/>\n<strong><em>D14:<\/em><\/strong><em> V\u0103n, <\/em><em>S\u1eed<\/em><em>, Ti\u1ebfng Anh, <strong>D1<\/strong><\/em><strong><em>5<\/em><\/strong><strong><em>:<\/em><\/strong><em> V\u0103n, \u0110\u1ecba, Ti\u1ebfng Anh.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><strong>2.2<em>. Thi tuy\u1ec3n<\/em><\/strong><br \/>\nM\u00f4n thi: C\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, C\u01a1 s\u1edf ng\u00e0nh, Chuy\u00ean ng\u00e0nh<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3. Th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp to\u00e0n kh\u00f3a<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3.1.<em> Th\u1eddi gian <\/em><\/strong><br \/>\n<span style=\"background-color: white;\">&#8211; Nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1: T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>17\/10\/2022<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>05\/11\/2022<\/strong><br \/>\n&#8211; X\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n\/Thi tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): ng\u00e0y <strong>08\/11\/2022<\/strong><br \/>\n&#8211; Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): ng\u00e0y <strong>15\/11\/2022<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3.2. L\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong> (t\u00f9y theo \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p): <strong>1.5 n\u0103m<\/strong><br \/>\n<strong><em>Th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n.<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>4. L\u00ea\u0323 phi\u0301<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&#8211; H\u1ed3 s\u01a1: mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&#8211; L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed x\u00e9t tuy\u1ec3n: <strong>1.200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/strong>\/1 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>5. H\u00f4\u0300 s\u01a1:<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&#8211; Phi\u1ebfu \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi (theo m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4);<\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&#8211; B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ec7 trung c\u1ea5p ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf l\u00ean;<\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&#8211; B\u1ea3n sao gi\u1ea5y khai sinh, CMT\/CCCD,gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd \u01b0u ti\u00ean (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3), 04 \u1ea3nh 4&#215;6<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>6. \u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/strong><br \/>\n&gt;&gt;C\u00e1ch 1: Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n ph\u00e1t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh &#8211; Hotline<\/strong><strong>: <\/strong><strong>0934.078.668, 02433.861.601<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">Km 15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">(C\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110H C\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Khoa h\u1ecdc Qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u00a0800m)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">&gt;&gt; C\u00e1ch 2: Tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn:\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone\" style=\"height: 26px; width: 120px;\" title=\"dangkyngay-3\" src=\"http:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/dangkyngay-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"190\" height=\"41\" \/><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\